Adorned in a light blue lehenga, the girl exudes an ethereal aura. The delicate fabric drapes gracefully, swaying with every step she takes. The soothing hue of the lehenga complements her complexion, casting a soft radiance. Intricate silver and white embroidery dances across the fabric, adding a touch of opulence to her attire. The blouse showcases a subtle neckline, allowing her natural elegance to shine. As she moves, the soft shimmer of the lehenga catches the light, creating an enchanting play of luminosity. With every detail thoughtfully curated, she embodies a blend of tradition and modern grace.

latestPosts.caption:
Sundays are for slow sips & soulful bites…
Brunched at Bastian, Pune and the vibe was just so me — cozy, elegant, and deliciously indulgent.
We tried the Korean Fried Chicken & Lamb Ghee Roast (still dreaming of that btw), and the drinks? Watermelon Peach Cooler + ElderTea — refreshing, floral, calming.

But the real star… was the Pull-Up Hazelnut Crunch — gooey, rich, and such a drama queen of a dessert!

Definitely a spot for great food, luxe ambience, and dessert that melts your stress away.

Alsoooo, they’re now open for lunch from Thursday to Saturday — so go treat yourself!
